item.title: Heaven Village The village hidden in the Skies
item.content:encoded:
Hi my name is Belzhebu i recently make a village and i am looking for new player to join me

Come and join us, we concentrate in new players looking for help,
come and grow with us, i can help you with my knowledge, and together we can grow to be the best!, come and join us!

Greetings and salutations for you

And remember i'm looking for you.
